    <td><b>Break</b></td></tr>

  <tr VALIGN=TOP>
    <td>16:00 &mdash;<br/>16:30</td>
    <td><b>Discussion Groups Wrap-Up</b><br/>

        Each group concludes by preparing a "mini-report" or "outbrief" that
        summarizes the discussion: achievements, positions, opinions, common
        themes, closed issues, open issues, solved problems, challenge
        problems, ideas for future activities and collaborations, ....
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr VALIGN=TOP>
    <td>16:30 &mdash;<br/>17:30</td>
    <td><b>Discussion Group Reports</b><br/>

        Representatives of the discussion groups present their outbriefs to all
        the workshop attendees. The workshop concludes with planning of
        post-workshop activities.<br/><br/>

        <b>Conclude</b>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
